Dear Adam and Tamar,

I wanted to follow-up on investor reporting for the Coller PBN structure. P=
lease see attached for the Q1-21 distribution report published by the struc=
ture=E2=80=99s trustee, Bank of New York Mellon. This report provides a sum=
mary of the structure including payments as well as the performance of the =
underlying Coller International Partners VIII fund. We are happy to find so=
me time to walk you through the report and the performance of the fund in d=
etail, if helpful.

This report is provided on a quarterly basis and can be accessed directly v=
ia the Bank of New York Mellon online investor reporting platform. Please s=
ee below steps for creating a profile and gaining access to the platform. I=
 have also copied in Daniel and Adrian from the BNY Mellon team who can ass=
ist with the next steps. Please let us know if we can help coordinate this =
with your administrator/The Service.

=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D


  1.  Investor reports can be accessed through the following website: https=
://gctinvestorreporting.bnymellon.com  (Register Now link)
  2.  Upon receipt of the request and validation by the BNY Mellon team, yo=
ur access will be approved
  3.  A request for deal access to view CIP VIII PBN, and a separate reques=
t to view the reports is required

=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D


Kind regards,
Mehmet


